node.text: A $7,000,000 Diamond Watch by Jacob & Co 💎✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by IFLW on September 03, 2021. May be an image of wrist watch.

node.text:
The incredible @jacobandco Mystery Tourbillon Rainbow rose gold🌈 💎

This masterpiece in a 18K rose gold case features eye-catching dial flawlessly set with hexagonal, overlapping multi colored shades sapphires.

It also features an incredible Twin Triple Axis Tourbillon and it shows the time by through the two ”mystery” rotating discs set with rubies, diamonds and sapphires.

The total carat weight is a crazy 45 cts 🤩

node.text:
The @jacobandco Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon Pavé Rose Gold ✨💎

419 brilliant round diamonds adorns the Rose Gold Case of this complicated timepiece. 

The Sapphire crystal reveals the entirety of the movement, including its W16 “engine,” the one-minute tourbillon and the power reserve indicator at 9 o’clock, designed to look like fuel gauge.

The watch is designed to replicate and celebrate the Bugatti Chiron hyper sportscar. 

It’s part of an ongoing partnership between @jacobandco and Bugatti to produce watches that have never been seen before.

node.text:
Unboxing the @JacobAndCo Mystery Tourbillon Tsavorites 🟢💎

This jaw dropping masterpiece with a 18K white gold case features eye-catching dial flawlessly set with hexagonal, overlapping 454 white diamonds and 12 tsavorites.

Both the minute and the hour discs are set with a single red ruby to indicate the time of this striking piece.

The total carat weight is 35.41cts 👀

At the center of the Mystery Tsavorites are present Two Triple-Axis Tourbillons decorated with 2 rubies.

Limited Edition of 18 pieces and priced at $1,300,000 💸
